<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ server_name }} - Deployed with Ansible</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .status {
            background: rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid #2ecc71;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .info-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .info-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #3498db;
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #f39c12;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üöÄ Web Server Successfully Deployed!</h1>
            <p>Automated deployment with Ansible</p>
        </div>

        <div class="status">
            <h2>‚úÖ Deployment Status: SUCCESS</h2>
            <p>Deployed on: <span class="highlight">{{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>üñ•Ô∏è Server Information</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Hostname:</strong> {{ inventory_hostname }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Server Name:</strong> {{ server_name }}</li>
                    <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Operating System:</strong> {{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Architecture:</strong> {{ ansible_architecture }}</li>
                    <li><strong>CPU Cores:</strong> {{ ansible_processor_vcpus }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Memory:</strong> {{ (ansible_memtotal_mb / 1024) | round(1) }} GB</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>üåê Web Server Configuration</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Web Server:</strong> Nginx {{ nginx_version }}</li>
                    <li><strong>SSL/TLS:</strong> Enabled ({{ environments[ansible_env].ssl_protocols | default('TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3') }})</li>
                    <li><strong>Environment:</strong> {{ ansible_env | upper }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Worker Processes:</strong> {{ nginx_worker_processes }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Document Root:</strong> {{ document_root }}</li>
                    <li><strong>App User:</strong> {{ app_user }}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>üîí Security Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Firewall:</strong> UFW Enabled</li>
                    <li><strong>Allowed Ports:</strong> {{ firewall_allowed_ports | join(', ') }}</li>
                    <li><strong>SSL Certificate:</strong> {{ ssl_cert_file }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Security Headers:</strong> Enabled</li>
                    <li><strong>Server Tokens:</strong> Hidden</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>‚ö° Performance Settings</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Gzip Compression:</strong> Enabled</li>
                    <li><strong>Keep-Alive Timeout:</strong> {{ nginx_keepalive_timeout }}s</li>
                    <li><strong>Worker Connections:</strong> {{ nginx_worker_connections }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Client Max Body Size:</strong> {{ nginx_client_max_body_size }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Static File Caching:</strong> 1 year</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="status">
            <h3>üéØ Quick Tests</h3>
            <p>‚Ä¢ SSL Certificate: <a href="https://{{ server_name }}" style="color: #3498db;">https://{{ server_name }}</a></p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Security Headers: Check with security scanning tools</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Performance: Test with tools like GTmetrix or PageSpeed Insights</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.8;">
            <p>Deployed with ‚ù§Ô∏è using Ansible automation</p>
            <p>Deployment ID: {{ ansible_date_time.epoch }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>